00:02:44.740 --> 00:02:47.060
And it's supposed to be perpendicular to our plane.

00:02:47.240 --> 00:02:48.940
And our plane passes for the origin here.

00:02:50.800 --> 00:02:58.420
So we want to think of a plane that's perpendicular to this

00:02:58.420 --> 00:02:58.720
